<h1>Microcontroller Electric Oven</h1>

<h2>Description</h2>

Developed a temperature-controlled electric oven using an ATmega32 microcontroller. The system regulated heating based on user-defined settings and sensor feedback.

<br />

<h2>Project Objectives</h2>

- Control temperature accurately
- Implement user controls
- Monitor heating performance
- Develop an embedded control system

<h2>Process</h2>

- Designed the control architecture
- Programmed temperature regulation logic
- Interfaced sensors and heating elements
- Tested system performance

<h2>Skills Learned</h2>

- C Programming
- ATmega32
- Arduino IDE
- Embedded Systems
- Electronics Fundamentals
- Sensor Interfacing

<h2>Tools Used</h2>

- Arduino IDE
- ATmega32

